    "text": {
      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Henk Koppelaar</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:185px;\"><a href=\"https://tudelft.academia.edu/ProfKoppelaar\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/e/ed/HenkKoppelaar.jpg\" width=\"183\" height=\"231\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:HenkKoppelaar.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Henk Koppelaar <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Hendrik (Henk) Koppelaar</b>,<br />\na Dutch physicist, mathematician, computer scientist, <a href=\"/Artificial_Intelligence\" title=\"Artificial Intelligence\">AI</a> researcher and professor emeritus in CS and <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Knowledge_engineering\">knowledge engineering</a> at <a href=\"/Delft_University_of_Technology\" title=\"Delft University of Technology\">Delft University of Technology</a>, \nand before, assistant professor in <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Decision_support_system\">decision support systems</a> at Delft University of Technology, head of <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Data_processing\">data processing</a> at <a href=\"/Tilburg_University\" title=\"Tilburg University\">Tilburg University</a>, and assistant professor at <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Utrecht_University\">Utrecht University</a> in <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Statistics\">statistics</a> and <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mathematical_model\">mathematical modeling</a> \n<sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>. \nHe holds a Ph.D. in <a href=\"/Artificial_Intelligence\" title=\"Artificial Intelligence\">artificial intelligence</a> modeling techniques applied to <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Social_science\">social sciences</a> in 1984 from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/University_of_Amsterdam\">University of Amsterdam</a> \n<sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>, \nand his research interests in AI include <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Knowledge-based_systems\">knowledge based systems</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>, \n<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Expert_system\">expert systems</a> and <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Computational_linguistics\">computational linguistics</a>. \nIn the 70s, along with <a href=\"/Barend_Swets\" title=\"Barend Swets\">Barend Swets</a>, he worked and published on computer chess and artificial intelligence \n<sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>, \nand more recently, along with <a href=\"/index.php?title=Alex_B._Meijer&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Alex B. Meijer (page does not exist)\">Alex B. Meijer</a> on <a href=\"/Learning\" title=\"Learning\">learning</a> and <a href=\"/Planning\" title=\"Planning\">planning</a> in <a href=\"/Go\" title=\"Go\">Go</a> \n<sup id=\"cite_ref-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup>. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Selected_Publications\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Selected Publications</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#1970_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">1970 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#1980_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">1980 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#1990_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">1990 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#2000_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2000 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Selected_Publications\">Selected Publications</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Henk_Koppelaar&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Selected Publications\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p><sup id=\"cite_ref-7\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-8\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-8\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"1970_...\">1970 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Henk_Koppelaar&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 1970 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Henk Koppelaar</a> (<b>1974</b>). <i>Hypergeometric (Certification and Remark on Algorithm 191)</i>. <a href=\"/ACM#Communications\" title=\"ACM\">Communications of the ACM</a>, Vol. 17, No. 10 <sup id=\"cite_ref-9\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-9\">&#91;9&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-10\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-10\">&#91;10&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/pers/hd/k/Kickert:Walter_J=_M=\">Walter J. M. Kickert</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Henk Koppelaar</a> (<b>1976</b>). <i>Application of Fuzzy Set Theory to Syntactic Pattern Recognition of Handwritten Capitals</i>. <a href=\"/IEEE#SMC\" title=\"IEEE\">IEEE Transactions on Systems, Man, and Cybernetics</a>, Vol. 6, No. 2</li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Henk Koppelaar</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/pers/hd/m/Molenaar:Peter\">Peter Molenaar</a> (<b>1976</b>). <i>Remark on \"Algorithm 486: Numerical Inversion of Laplace Transform [D5]</i>. <a href=\"/ACM#TOMS\" title=\"ACM\">ACM Transactions on Mathematical Software</a>, Vol. 2, No. 4 <sup id=\"cite_ref-11\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-11\">&#91;11&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-12\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-12\">&#91;12&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Henk Koppelaar</a> (<b>1976</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dl.acm.org/doi/10.1145/1102766.1102768\">Geometric distribution generator</a></i>. <a href=\"/ACM#SIGSIM\" title=\"ACM\">ACM SIGSIM</a>, Vol. 8, No. 3</li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Barend_Swets\" title=\"Barend Swets\">Barend Swets</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Henk Koppelaar</a> (<b>1978</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.worldcat.org/title/schaken-met-kunstmatige-intelligente/oclc/769893277\">Schaken met Kunstmatige Intelligente</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Intermediair\">Intermediair</a>, Vol. 14, No. 19 (Dutch)</li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Barend_Swets\" title=\"Barend Swets\">Barend Swets</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Henk Koppelaar</a> (<b>1978</b>). <i>De Struktuur van Schaakprogrammas</i>. Informatie, Vol. 20, No. 6  (Dutch)</li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Barend_Swets\" title=\"Barend Swets\">Barend Swets</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Henk Koppelaar</a> (<b>1979</b>). <i>Schakend zand&#160;: de Chip als Toekomstig Schaak-Grootmeester</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Intermediair\">Intermediair</a>, Vol. 15, No. 24  (Dutch)</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"1980_...\">1980 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Henk_Koppelaar&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 1980 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Henk Koppelaar</a> (<b>1981</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dl.acm.org/doi/10.1145/1103225.1103230\">The Wenstøp language</a></i>. <a href=\"/ACM#SIGSIM\" title=\"ACM\">ACM SIGSIM</a>, Vol. 12, No. 1-4 <sup id=\"cite_ref-13\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-13\">&#91;13&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Henk Koppelaar</a> (<b>1984</b>). <i>Twee nieuwe wegen voor modelbouw in de sociale wetenschappen: theorie- en dataverwerking (English: Two new ways for modeling in the social sciences: theory and data processing)</i>. Ph.D. thesis, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/University_of_Amsterdam\">University of Amsterdam</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"1990_...\">1990 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Henk_Koppelaar&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: 1990 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.kbs.twi.tudelft.nl/People/Staff/E.J.H.Kerckhoffs/\">Eugene Kerckhoffs</a>, Martin van Raaij, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.tudelft.nl/en/tpm/about-the-faculty/professors/professor-profile/peter-kroes/\">Peter Kroes</a>, <a href=\"/Mathematician#LRothkrantz\" title=\"Mathematician\">Léon Rothkrantz</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Henk Koppelaar</a> (<b>1993</b>). <i>Hypercube implementation and performance of the Cascade-Correlation Learning Algorithm</i>. Proceedings of Neuronet</li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Henk Koppelaar</a> (<b>1996</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.worldcat.org/title/expert-system-for-generating-waveforms/oclc/59635001\">An Expert System for Generating Waveforms</a></i>. Report of the Faculty of Technical Mathematics and Informatics, <a href=\"/Delft_University_of_Technology\" title=\"Delft University of Technology\">Delft University of Technology</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Mathematician#MPantic\" title=\"Mathematician\">Maja Pantic</a>, <a href=\"/Mathematician#LRothkrantz\" title=\"Mathematician\">Léon Rothkrantz</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Henk Koppelaar</a> (<b>1998</b>). <i>Automation of Non-Verbal Communication of Facial Expressions</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.eurosis.org/cms/?q=taxonomy/term/22\">Euromedia'98</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://ibug.doc.ic.ac.uk/media/uploads/documents/Euromedia98.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> D. Chitchian, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://scholar.google.com/citations?user=AP0dawoAAAAJ&amp;hl=en\">Sevil Sariyildiz</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Henk Koppelaar</a> (<b>1999</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007%2F978-3-540-48765-4_77\">Architectural Knowledge Representation Using the Galois Lattice Technique</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/db/conf/ieaaie/ieaaie1999.html\">IEA/AIE 1999</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2000_...\">2000 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Henk_Koppelaar&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: 2000 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Alex_B._Meijer&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Alex B. Meijer (page does not exist)\">Alex B. Meijer</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Henk Koppelaar</a> (<b>2001</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.kbs.twi.tudelft.nl/Publications/Conference/2001/2001-MeijerKoppelaar-GAMEON01.html\">A learning architecture for the game of Go</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.org/db/conf/gameon/gameon2001\">Game-On 2001</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Alex_B._Meijer&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Alex B. Meijer (page does not exist)\">Alex B. Meijer</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Henk Koppelaar</a> (<b>2001</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.kbs.twi.tudelft.nl/Publications/Conference/2001/2001-MeijerKoppelaar-BNAIC01.html\">Pursuing abstract goals in the game of Go</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.org/db/conf/bnaic/index\">BNAIC 2001</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Alex_B._Meijer&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Alex B. Meijer (page does not exist)\">Alex B. Meijer</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Henk Koppelaar</a> (<b>2003</b>). <i>Towards Multi-Objective Game Theory - with Application to Go</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.eurosis.org/conf/gameon/gameon2003/index.html\">Game-On 2003</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.mmi.tudelft.nl/pub/alex/meijer-gameon03.pdf\">pdf</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Henk_Koppelaar&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://tudelft.academia.edu/ProfKoppelaar\">Henk Koppelaar | Delft University of Technology - Academia.edu</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://genealogy.math.ndsu.nodak.edu/id.php?id=168356\">The Mathematics Genealogy Project - Hendrik (Henk) Koppelaar</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://scholar.google.nl/citations?user=TqrS2goAAAAJ&amp;hl=en\">H. Koppelaar - Google Scholar Citations</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.kbs.twi.tudelft.nl/\">Knowledge Based Systems Group</a>, <a href=\"/Delft_University_of_Technology\" title=\"Delft University of Technology\">TU Delft</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Henk_Koppelaar&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap mw-references-columns\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://tudelft.academia.edu/ProfKoppelaar\">Henk Koppelaar | Delft University of Technology - Academia.edu</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/pub/henk-koppelaar-2000/9/a1b/7a3\">Henk Koppelaar (2000+) | LinkedIn</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Henk Koppelaar</a> (<b>1984</b>). <i>Twee nieuwe wegen voor modelbouw in de sociale wetenschappen: theorie- en dataverwerking (English: Two new ways for modeling in the social sciences: theory and data processing)</i>. Ph.D. thesis, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/University_of_Amsterdam\">University of Amsterdam</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.kbs.twi.tudelft.nl/\">Knowledge Based Systems Group</a>, <a href=\"/Delft_University_of_Technology\" title=\"Delft University of Technology\">TU Delft</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/Barend_Swets\" title=\"Barend Swets\">Barend Swets</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Henk Koppelaar</a> (<b>1978</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.worldcat.org/title/schaken-met-kunstmatige-intelligente/oclc/769893277\">Schaken met Kunstmatige Intelligente</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://nl.wikipedia.org/wiki/Intermediair_%28tijdschrift%29\">Intermediair</a>, Vol. 14, No. 19  (Dutch)</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/index.php?title=Alex_B._Meijer&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Alex B. Meijer (page does not exist)\">Alex B. Meijer</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Henk Koppelaar</a> (<b>2001</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.kbs.twi.tudelft.nl/Publications/Conference/2001/2001-MeijerKoppelaar-GAMEON01.html\">A learning architecture for the game of Go</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.org/db/conf/gameon/gameon2001\">Game-On 2001</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-7\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/pers/hd/k/Koppelaar:Henk\">dblp: Henk Koppelaar</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-8\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-8\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://scholar.google.nl/citations?user=TqrS2goAAAAJ&amp;hl=en\">H. Koppelaar - Google Scholar Citations</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-9\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-9\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/pers/hd/r/Relph:A=_P=.html\">A. P. Relph</a> (<b>1963</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dl.acm.org/doi/10.1145/366663.366680\">Algorithm 191: hypergeometric</a></i>. <a href=\"/ACM#Communications\" title=\"ACM\">Communications of the ACM</a>, Vol. 6, No. 7</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-10\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-10\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hypergeometric_function\">Hypergeometric function from Wikipedia</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-11\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-11\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dl.acm.org/profile/81538472456\">Francoise Veillon</a> (<b>1974</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dl.acm.org/doi/10.1145/355620.361174\">Algorithm 486: Numerical inversion of Laplace transform D5</a></i>. <a href=\"/ACM#Communications\" title=\"ACM\">Communications of the ACM</a>, Vol. 17, No. 10</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-12\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-12\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Laplace_transform\">Laplace transform from Wikipedia</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-13\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-13\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://no.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fred_Wenst%C3%B8p\">Fred Wenstøp</a> (<b>1978</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007%2F978-3-642-93104-8_242\">Verbal Formulation of Fuzzy Dynamic Systems</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.springer.com/gp/book/9783642931062\">Current Topics in Cybernetics and Systems</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260228223650\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.026 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.027 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 213/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 466/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key oscar70_mw1-mw_:pcache:idhash:6694-0!canonical and timestamp 20260228223650 and revision id 22090\n -->\n"
